parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective valve can cause the burner to remain on, posing a fire hazard, and require the propane tank to be turned off to shut off the burner, which can be dangerous and inconvenient.
symptoms: The valve locks up
the burner cannot be turned off
the valve must be cooled off before it can be turned off
the stove/range fails to work properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hydraulic leak can cause the slide-out unit to malfunction, leading to difficulties with extending or retracting the unit, and potentially causing damage to the surrounding structure.
symptoms: Hydraulic fluid leak
slide-out unit malfunction
difficulty extending or retracting the unit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sewer system knife valves can cause sewage to leak, leading to unsanitary conditions, unpleasant odors, and potential health hazards.
symptoms: Sewer system malfunction
sewage leak
unpleasant odors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the Firestone SteelTex tire can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowout
tire tread separation
tire shredding
damage to the underside of the vehicle
damage to surrounding components such as fuel lines and gas caps.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed Repair of Cruise Control Switch under Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed repair of the cruise control switch under recall can cause inconvenience and discomfort to drivers who rely on the feature for medical reasons, potentially leading to driver fatigue and decreased safety on the road.
symptoms: Unavailability of cruise control feature
delayed repair of recalled part
uncertainty about repair timeline.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty parking brake can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The parking brake does not engage or disengage properly
the parking brake lever or pedal feels loose or spongy
the vehicle rolls or moves while parked on an incline
the parking brake warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gray water tank support can cause the tank to fall to the ground, potentially leading to a major accident, especially if it occurs while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The gray water tank support breaks
causing the tank to fall to the ground
potentially resulting in damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The poor design of the tank supports (both gray water and waste water) can lead to a safety hazard, potentially causing accidents or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The tank supports break or fail
causing the tanks to fall to the ground
potentially resulting in damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
